data.description: SELLER'S MOTIVATED! Welcome to your waterfront retreat in Salt Springs, Florida! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bath home, nestled in Marion County, offers a perfect blend of comfort, modern amenities, and serene natural beauty. As you approach this lovely residence, the first thing you'll notice is the pride of ownership. A new roof installed in 2018 ensures worry-free living, providing both durability and peace of mind. New heat pump installed that provides both air & heat to ensure a cool summer and cozy winter. There are wall units as well to give an extra boost of cool air if needed.  The heart of the home is the kitchen, where granite countertops and a pantry add a touch of elegance and convenience. One of the standout features of this property is its prime waterfront location. Situated on a tranquil canal that leads out to the breathtaking Lake George, you'll have the privilege of witnessing stunning sunsets. Additional amenities include a small shed, perfect for storing outdoor equipment and tools, and easy access to a community boat ramp. For those who appreciate water-based activities, this home provides an ideal gateway to boating, fishing, and exploring the pristine waters of Lake George. Call to schedule your private tour today!
